README for polybar


INSTALL


  Get started with the example configuration:

  $ cp /usr/share/polybar/config.example $HOME/.config/polybar/config
  $ polybar example


  For more information, see https://github.com/polybar/polybar/wiki


CUSTOMIZE BUILD


  This port comes with a minimal set of polybar modules. Supported modules
  will vary depending of your installation and features detected during the
  build.

  --  Module support:
  -- [X]   alsa
  -- [X]   curl
  -- [ ]   i3
  -- [ ]   mpd
  -- [X]   network (libnl)
  -- [ ]   pulseaudio
  -- [X]   xkeyboard

